summary: my first try on the creation kit...sorry for this sincere saying ^^\'
descriptionHtml:
I wanted to start over a nice quest mod but thought that I need to practice first.
This mod is my first try to do my main Skyrim character- a khajiit tank.
Since she is my first creation- I didn\'t do other dialogues and such but I would like to do that in the future- maybe with some voiceacting

well, she is also a person who likes dwemer ruins, can do Unrelenting Force and Fire Breath; and appreciates imperials  doesn\'t like stormcloaks and hates the thalmor 0_o
She is at the Silver Blood Inn in Markarth
A nice companion for characters from 20+lvl
author: Gureii
